&lt;h3 id="2-edge-computing-and-cdns">2. Edge Computing and CDNs&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Moving computation closer to users:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Getting Started with Hugo: A Beginner's Guide</title><link>https://dev--200rx.netlify.app/posts/getting-started-with-hugo/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dev--200rx.netlify.app/posts/getting-started-with-hugo/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Hugo is one of the fastest static site generators available today. Built with Go, it can generate thousands of pages in seconds, making it perfect for blogs, documentation sites, and portfolios.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="why-choose-hugo">Why Choose Hugo?&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="speed">Speed&lt;/h3>
